{"tid":2294362,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"荷里活最環保嘅迪士尼又一翻拍之作 今次輪到史迪仔套《扮嘢小魔星》","createTime":"2020-11-21T03:28:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T16:51:23.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"20266ea84b258e7fd8f05810ad2b543b0ba99951","tid":2294362,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T03:28:24.000Z","msg":"相信成個荷里活最環保嘅片廠一定係迪士尼，係循環再造方面無人能及！繼《獅子王》、《小飛象》、《阿拉丁》、《小魚仙》、《花木蘭》等等之後，最新循環再拍嘅有史迪仔！<br />\n<br />\n講緊嘅環保係迪士尼有幾不遺餘力翻用自己嘅經典動畫、電影故事，將庫存劇目重拍一次，動畫就將佢真人化，本身係真人版嘅就重拍一次！傳聞迪士尼翻拍2002年動畫《扮嘢小魔星》真人版己久，依家終於落實計劃。據外媒Variety報導，迪士尼已經同《我的超豪男友》導演朱浩偉（Jon Chu）傾得八八九九，將會由佢執導新版史迪仔。"},{"pid":"a52b5668861fff981df18f753497c7c182cb1e92","tid":2294362,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T03:30:29.000Z","msg":"當年《扮》海報一出都幾轟動，皆因史迪仔大耳大口加尖牙嘅外貌顛覆咗合家歡動畫固有嘅可愛、得意形象，仲有少少怪！故事講述小女孩Lilo收養咗一隻外表趣怪嘅寵物，並為佢改名做史迪仔，其實史迪仔真身係外星生物，誤打誤撞結果被Lilo當成狗仔收養！Lilo同史迪仔好快建立起深厚友誼，就算之後面對大圍捕遇險，Lilo都堅持同史迪仔共患難，因為家人係唔會放棄彼此嘅！<br />\n<br />\n正因為佢同Lilo真摰友誼太感動，睇完戲後無人再覺得史迪仔怪樣，觀感大變成為人見人愛角色，依家仲係迪士尼樂園其中一隻受歡迎嘅角色添，周邊商品出極都咁好賣！<br />\n<br />\n朱浩偉嘅《我的超豪男友》上映時喺美國引起好大迴響，除咗廿幾年嚟首次全亞裔荷里活商業大片，當中嘅奢華排場、麻雀變鳳凰嘅故事都睇得人好興奮，美國人其實都好鍾意睇有錢仔戀上窮家女故事！不過，最精彩一定要數女主角Rachael同未來奶奶打麻雀鬆章一幕，TVB得嚟又好講到亞洲家庭文化精髓，《我》咁高難度都搞得掂，相信翻拍《扮嘢小魔星》一定勝任有餘！"},{"pid":"189c8817cd8c091c26b5ba49bdae351499e880f5","tid":2294362,"uid":110456,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T03:32:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mzqzY0p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmzqzY0p.jpg&h=8a306a24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"badf822c8cbd626a2ed87648b4d6826c025bc56c","tid":2294362,"uid":171849,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T03:35:40.000Z","msg":"成套野有一半都係動物喎<br />\n搵人扮定變卡通？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KsCyu7H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKsCyu7H.jpg&h=3edb5b67&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b73147b67eecda8959333a1b3d1e08c685fadc2f","tid":2294362,"uid":236359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T03:38:56.000Z","msg":"好似好多女鍾意史迪仔"},{"pid":"e0773ff794dc9a6927f308d8be4b1831c0eca4d6","tid":2294362,"uid":313584,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T03:42:12.000Z","msg":"係咪搵the rock做黑超社工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012d1a09a4520280c39f705ebac0fe38707d4868","tid":2294362,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"189c8817cd8c091c26b5ba49bdae351499e880f5","tid":2294362,"uid":110456,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T03:32:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mzqzY0p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmzqzY0p.jpg&h=8a306a24&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T03:43:22.000Z","msg":"嘩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8eaaa519474f80ffcab3a3a67b85f77df200cd8","tid":2294362,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"012d1a09a4520280c39f705ebac0fe38707d4868","tid":2294362,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"189c8817cd8c091c26b5ba49bdae351499e880f5","tid":2294362,"uid":110456,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T03:32:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mzqzY0p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmzqzY0p.jpg&h=8a306a24&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T03:43:22.000Z","msg":"嘩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T16:51:23.000Z","msg":"雖然知道應該係fans made ，但史迪仔真人化左真係好難會可愛喎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}